+ * Radio tuning for Maxim max2820 on RTL8180
+ *
+ * Copyright 2007 Andrea Merello <andreamrl@tiscali.it>
+ *
+ * Code from the BSD driver and the rtl8181 project have been
+ * very useful to understand certain things
